             was indicted for <rs id="t18101031-21-off124" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18101031-21-off124" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18101031-21-off124" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously forging, on the <rs id="t18101031-21-cd125" type="crimeDate">9th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-21-off124 t18101031-21-cd125"></join>, an order for the payment of 103 l. 12 s. with intention to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18101031-21-victim324" type="victimName">
                           Westgurth 
                           Snaith
                        <interp inst="t18101031-21-victim324" type="surname" value="Snaith"></interp>
